OL,3,C'I was forced to do so' ` alleged
OL,4,CChannel small boat pilot tells court
OL,6,FAn Afghan national has denied
OL,7,Fendangering 46 people during a boat
OL,8,Fcrossing to the UK as he told the
OL,9,Fcourt: "I plead not guilty, I was
OL,10,Fforced to do so".
OL,12,FAman Naseri appeared at Margate
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday after
OL,14,Fbeing charged with endangerment of
OL,15,Flife during a small boat crossing of
OL,16,Fthe English Channel.
OL,18,FIt's the first alleged offence of its
OL,19,Fkind since it became law on January 5.
