OL,3,C'I was forced to do so' ` alleged
OL,4,CChannel small boat pilot tells court
OL,6,FWearing a black coat in the dock, the
OL,7,F18-year-old, who followed proceedings
OL,8,Fthrough a Dari interpreter, also spoke
OL,9,Fto confirm his name and date of birth
OL,10,Fduring a short hearing.
OL,12,FHe was remanded into custody to appear
OL,13,Fat Canterbury Crown Court on Friday.
OL,15,FThe new offence is part of a range of
OL,16,Fmeasures introduced to curb Channel
OL,17,Fcrossings which came into force under
OL,18,Fthe Border Security, Asylum and
OL,19,FImmigration Act which became law in
OL,20,FDecember.
